                  <summary><p>Incomplete: KV + 1–351.7 (missing: 158.7ff.–172, 204, page number 47/48 omitted).</p>
<p>Head colophon with marginal blessing in grantha (<q xml:lang="ta"><term xml:lang="sa">hariḥ om</term> naṉṟāka</q>) with four devotional <term xml:lang="sa">Vaiṣṇava</term> stanzas and a series of blessings (902 k°22 <q xml:lang="ta">kārttikai māta mutal reṅkanātaṉ eḻuti varukiṟatu...caṅkattār pāṭiya neṭuṅtokaiyum tuṟaiyuṅ kavi pāṭiṉ pērkaḷum eḻutiyirukkutu. makiḻmāṟavar taṉ malar aṭiyē tañcam. <term xml:lang="sa">śubham astu. <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/>rāma jayam. keruṭāya namaḥ.</term></q>). </p>
<p>Scribal errors are comparatively few, many blank spaces, in length between <term xml:lang="sa">akṣara</term>-s and several <term xml:lang="ta">cīr</term>; second representative of the second strand of transmission; closely agreeing with C2.</p>
<p>The more recent images of this manuscript from the Tamil Digital Library are missing folios 1v and 2v.</p></summary>
                  
